description:
G-Wrench finds Mona, but their reunions is sullied by Mona`s strange behavior. She doesn`t seem to recognize G-Wrench, and even attacks her! Unable to fight back, G-Wrench just calls out to her, desperately. Meanwhile, Cleanette, watching the battle, realizes something...
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: アジャスト・G ・レンチ
